+			<title>
+				<function moreinfo="none">pv_xavp_to_var(xname)</function>
+			</title>
+			<para>
+				Copy xavp values to vars. Reverse of pv_var_to_xavp().
+			</para>
+			<para>
+			Function can be used from ANY_ROUTE.
+			</para>
